data.title: The Football Association of Hong Kong, China Limited
data.meta_description: 中國香港足球總會所肩負的使命是進一步推動本港足球事業和提升目前足球發展水平
data.text:
Hong Kong, China U20 Representative Team will participate in a training camp from 2 to 10 June 2024. The preliminary squad with 39 players is as follow:

Goalkeepers

SHEK Tuscany (Kitchee), James Robert WRIGHT (HKFC), HUI Pak Wai Arsene (Kwoon Chung Southern), POON Sheung Hei (Lee Man), MAK Tsz Hin (RCFC)

Field Players

CHAN Joe Yiu Cho, CHIU Ching Yu Sergio (BC Rangers), CHAN Max (Boreham Wood FC), WU Moses (Brinkumer SV), WONG Hung Chi (Central & Western District), CHAN Ho Ka, DAI Tsz Hin Marcus (Crownity North District), CHEUNG Man Ho, LAM Chin Yu, LEE Chun Ting, LIU Hing Yau, LUI Tsz Kiu Jeremy, SIU Chung Nam, YEUNG Tung Ki (Eastern), CHOW Timothy Stephen (HKFC), LO Chun Hin, MA Chin Ho (HKU23), LAU Yu Ho, Matthew Luke SLATTERY, PANG Hing Hei, YEUNG Cheuk Kwan, YUEN Chun Him (Kitchee), HON Shing Wing, JIM Ho Chun, WONG Long Kaa Jan (Lee Man), LEE Ching, TSANG Chun Hin (RCFC), WONG Andy Clement (South China), LIANG Ngai Tung, WONG Shum Chit Sherman (Sham Shui Po), CHAN Kwan Ching Osmond, HO Tung Lam, LEUNG Yui Ching, TSANG Lok To Jeremy
